What Makes Us Unique

We are a boutique investment management firm focused exclusively on helping our clients to reach their financial goals. We are known for our dedicated client service. 
 We are independent and do not have affiliated investment banking or brokerage arms which could conflict with our focus on our clients best interests.          
Our incisive written analysis of macroeconomic and financial issues provides the framework for asset allocation and informs sector and specific investment selections. Clients know where we stand on economic and investment issues.          
Our singular focus allows us to be decisive and nimble- attributes of particular value in tumultuous times.          
We work hard to earn our clients trust through a dedicated focus on their needs and integrity in our decision making.          
We offer multiple investment strategies which can be combined to meet each client’s goals. 

Our structure provides additional peace of mind for clients

BSWMG manages client assets. We do not hold them. 
          
Your investments are held at a custodian of your choosing, in separate accounts, held in the legal title of those accounts.              


You receive separate statements of holdings and confirmations of transactions directly from this separate custodian. 
          
This data flows into our portfolio management system which is reconciled daily by the portfolio management software firm with the data available at your custodian. Reconciliations are performed on a best-efforts basis. 
            The securities underlying your account’s performance are independently visible on the custodial statements so that anyone viewing them could ascertain their likelihood of generating the stated performance.                    


We do not receive commissions on the transactions made in your accounts. We are solely compensated via fees based upon your account’s valuation. 
          
Unlike some managers that charge fees and commissions, we forego the extra commission revenue to obviate any actual, as well as potential conflicts of interest in our investments for you.              


We do not have the ability to move money outside of your accounts in your name with the exception of management fees.  We do this for your protection and for ours.        
Integrity and transparency provide a true value proposition for the client.        




 



