Fixed Income
Barrington Strategic Wealth Management Group manages both Taxable and Tax-Exempt Fixed income portfolios.  We tailor our portfolios based upon your income needs, risk tolerance, and long term goals.  Municipals, Treasuries, Corporates, Agencies and High Yield are among the fixed income vehicles utilized to create a diversified fixed income ladder.  Typically we maintain a 5-6 year duration but will extend or reduce based upon the market environment.  Risk, ratings and the current economic climate are all reviewed continually to maximize selection and ensure original fixed income guidelines and parameters are adhered to.



 



