About Barrington Wealth Management
At Barrington Wealth Management we believe that each person has a unique way they can enrich their world.  We believe that putting in place appropriate financial plans and a prudent investment strategy, allows clients the freedom and leverage to pursue a more meaningful life.  We work with a select group of individuals and families that are interested in a long term relationship that allows planning to be completed and dreams and goals to be clarified and pursued.
Barrington Wealth Management is an independent wealth management firm based in Barrington, Illinois.  With over 28 years of business experience and as an alliance partner of Carson Institutional Alliance, a Turnkey Integrated Partnership, we have the advantage of wisdom, dedicated knowledge and an extremely deep bench.
 

Core Values
At Barrington Wealth Management, we stay true to our core values, mission and vision so you can benefit from our commitment to help you enrich your world.

