Company Overview of Barrington Strategic Wealth Management Group LLC



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Barrington Strategic Wealth Management Group LLC is an employee owned investment manager. The firm primarily provides its services to high net worth individuals. It also caters to banking or thrift institutions, pension and profit sharing plans, charitable organizations, corporations, and other businesses. The firm manages separate client-focused equity, fixed income, and balanced portfolios. It invests in the public equity and fixed income markets across the globe. The firm primarily invests in growth and value stocks across all market capitalization ranging from $200 million to over $50 billion having maturity from 3 to 5 years. It uses a combination of fundamental and quantitative analysi...
Barrington Strategic Wealth Management Group LLC is an employee owned investment manager. The firm primarily provides its services to high net worth individuals. It also caters to banking or thrift institutions, pension and profit sharing plans, charitable organizations, corporations, and other businesses. The firm manages separate client-focused equity, fixed income, and balanced portfolios. It invests in the public equity and fixed income markets across the globe. The firm primarily invests in growth and value stocks across all market capitalization ranging from $200 million to over $50 billion having maturity from 3 to 5 years. It uses a combination of fundamental and quantitative analysis with top-down and bottom-up stock picking approach. The firm also invests in instruments like exchange traded funds and employs short and long/short strategies to create its portfolio. For its fixed income portion of the portfolio, it invests in securities issued by municipals, treasuries, corporate and agencies, mortgage backed securities, and global and high yield bonds. The firm invests in Dividend stocks. It typically invests in diversified sectors. Barrington Strategic Wealth Management Group LLC was founded in May, 2009 and is based in Chicago, Illinois.
Detailed Description


